      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "An off-market sale is a property transaction that occurs without the property being publicly listed on the major real estate portals. The sale happens through an agent's private buyer network, database marketing, or direct introduction — without the property appearing on realestate.com.au or domain.com.au."
      }
