      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How do I find off-market properties in Brisbane to buy?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Buyers access off-market opportunities by registering with specific agents who have strong private networks in the suburbs they want. A buyer's agent can also provide access to off-market stock. Simply being in an agent's database and communicating clearly about what you are looking for is the most reliable way to be considered for off-market introductions."
      }
    }
  ]
